Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.91,0:00:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.17,0:00:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- That was a close shave, wasn't it?\N- Claudia!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Erenshkigal...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ophélia!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So then I passed out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.66,0:00:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're finally up, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't wake up\Nfor three days straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You had me worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.59,0:00:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.80,0:00:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These two must've really been worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They've been hovering\Nover you every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.76,0:00:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should show them\Nyour appreciation later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:01:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I never thanked you myself, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that not only Ophélia,\Nbut even Gustave showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.\NSeriously, you saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you're not going to say\N"I'm indebted to you" now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to make sure\NI thanked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.70,0:01:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.79,0:01:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,how about telling me about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your relationship with that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.21,0:01:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ophélia Landlufen...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You remember this, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.30,0:01:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the handkerchief everybody\Nat the orphanage embroidered for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.60,0:01:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and your best friend sewed for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.81,0:01:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She didn't like fighting...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and she was a truly kind-hearted girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.99,0:01:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The one who sewed this for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...was Ophélia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:36.05,ArcName,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reunion
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What on earth is so fun\Nabout doing that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}See, plants are really honest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you suffuse them with love,\Nthey'll love you right back,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but if you neglect them,\Nthey'll abandon you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Abandon? Plants... abandon humans?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Plants that aren't even sick\Nwither and die{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}because they've had it with humans.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There was nothing she enjoyed\Nmore than caring for plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn't even bring herself\Nto kill an insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever beautiful flowers\Ncame into bloom,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,she would get so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what about yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That gutted building you saw\Non the snowy plain yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,was the result of Ophélia going berserk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It used to be an Integrated Enterprise\NFoundation lab called Frauenlob...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...where an Arlequint student\Nknown as the Magnum Opus
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,once conducted\Na certain kind of research.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Namely...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,creating manufactured Genestella.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the guinea pig for this experiment...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,was the person they took away\Nas collateral for the orphanage's debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ophélia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:04:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As a result,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ophélia, who wasn't even\Na member of the Genestella,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is now the most powerful\NStrega in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that the research\Nwas successful?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To this day, the ground below that\Nabandoned building is rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not even so much as a blade\Nof grass will grow there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The price she had to pay\Nfor the power she'd gained...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...was the inability to even go\Nnear those flowers she loved so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw her again in Asterisk,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I could see that she had changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was as if she'd given up on her past\Nand herself, and abandoned everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:34.66,Broadast,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OPHÉLIA!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:37.38,Broadast,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'M NOT ASKING YOU TO COME BACK!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:39.79,Broadast,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BUT... AT LEAST...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ophélia's uncommonly intense power\Nis a double-edged sword
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:43.17,Broadast,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,STOP FIGHTING
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that eats away at her,\Nthe more she uses it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:45.59,Broadast,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RECKLESSLY!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:48.64,Broadast,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IF YOU WANT YOUR WISH TO COME TRUE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to stop her\Nfrom further recklessness, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:51.06,Broadast,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FIGHT ME... AND...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:53.48,Broadast,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DEFEAT ME...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The result was... well, I shouldn't\Nhave to spell it out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I dragged you into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But now I'm going to\Nfinish this on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, Ophélia would never get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, you two\Nplaying possum over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you were onto us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we need to make\NGustave Marlowe our top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Has he attacked anyone else since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. You don't have to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've raised the threat level\Nthroughout the capital
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and we've bolstered\Nour security forces significantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just in case, I had them send some\Nforces over to the orphanage, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If he does show his face\Nsomewhere, it would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-B-B-Bad news, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flora? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you panicking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something is wrong with the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are all these giant lizard things,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,about this big, flying through the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are those things attacking people?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, not quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since the entire police force\Nis dealing with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there hasn't been\Na lot of damage yet, for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The entire force, did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So the police unit guarding\Nthe orphanage as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I hear they've all\Ngone into the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gustave knows what he's doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They wouldn't think twice\Nabout forsaking the orphanage,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and that this would be a good\Ndiversionary tactic to draw us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no doubt\Nhe's lying in wait in the slums.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if I don't show up, he's sure to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is my problem to fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Julis?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it's not just you\Nwho they're after, Julis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're involved in this one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will you follow my instructions exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gustave Marlowe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, Your Highness,\NPrincess Julis...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am humbled that you would\Ncome all this way to meet me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You better not have\Ntouched the orphanage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it would be pointless to destroy\Nthe bait before I even get my prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My first order of business\Nis to draw you all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a Hydra?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly right, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every bit as...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.99,0:09:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,no, even more imposing and striking\Nthan the ones in mythology, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Having lured my prey here,\NI have no more use for that bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't I finish this off\Nwithout further delay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, if you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I encourage you to enjoy\Nyourselves to the fullest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.23,0:10:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I want to protect the city,\NI've got to stop this thing, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since the police unit isn't showing up,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,our only choice is to do\Nsomething about this ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.13,0:10:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis, I want you to help\Nthe residents evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're going off\Nto stop that thing by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And anyway, Saya should be done\Nwith her preparations soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're more familiar\Nwith this area than I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone would listen\Nto you, wouldn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But make sure\Nyou don't do anything reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So there's no question about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can send you the evidence\NI've gathered if you need me to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, that won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's as far as you're gonna go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And now I stop you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So it regenerates, too, like in the myth?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ayato!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:11:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good save!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is that snake-thing my target?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's the plan?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.15,0:12:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gustave was serious\Nabout reproducing the myth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that until we chop off\Nthe head in the center,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the other heads around it\Nwill keep regenerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So a swift attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right. I'm gonna have\Nthis monitor on stand-by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. All right, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, that's two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}4 o'clock!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's four!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}6 o'clock.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm on it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That makes six!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya, let's finish it off\Nwith the next blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotcha.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amagiri Shinmei Style...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Twin Dragons!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that leaves just one!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato! 3 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did it speed up the regeneration\Nby focusing on just one head?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did such a great job, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done setting up my ploy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come out...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rafflesia Duoflores!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:14:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm at a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did you find me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.11,0:15:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surely someone like you\Nwould be watching
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,from where you could\Noverlook the entire slum,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,somewhere safe and not so far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's how Julis guessed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see... You certainly are a group\Nof annoyingly smart young girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kirin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've captured him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gustave Marlowe has been apprehended.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.57,0:15:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while\Nsince we last met, Claudia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A member of Galaxy hires a criminal\Nto assault a Seidoukan student...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a princess, no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy had nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I acted solely on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such an excuse wouldn't work\Nfor a man of your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that would also\Nbe my mother's judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If she deems it necessary, she won't\Nhesitate to throw me under the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, none of this\Nwill be of any use to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you know what will\Nhappen then, don't you, Claudia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you still insist on competing\Nin the Gryps Festa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At least change your wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's still time if you act now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I've already told you\Nnumerous times,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Claudia...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.68,0:16:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am truly grateful for all\Nthat you did for my sake, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:17:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really, thank you\Nfor all that you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, peace has been\Nrestored in our nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The people are deeply grateful as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, Julis...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the people in the old city\Nmight throw you another parade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that your position\Nwill soon become tenuous?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take this opportunity\Nto tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to win the Gryps Festa
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and expand the king's powers\Nin Lieseltania!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This incident convinced me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That in order to change this country,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to do something\Nat a more fundamental level.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, the Festa prize money\Ncould expand the king's powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it happens, I'm going to\Nburden and trouble you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But knowing all that...\NI'm asking you, Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you could\Nhelp me out, for my sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've really changed, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I never dreamed the day would come\Nthat you'd ask me for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is all thanks to you, Amagiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,no, all of you, I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You got it, Julis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you really do manage\Nto win the Gryps Festa,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then I'm going to go all-in\Nand stop being a good-for-nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.95,0:18:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're such a lovely\Nbrother and sister, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Steering Committee Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amagiri...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:18:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've found your sister.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Sis...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:07.23,Loc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ASTERISK CENTRAL DISTRICT - HOSPITAL
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka Amagiri was brought\Nin here five years or so ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her body's been in a state\Nof apparent death since that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.24,0:19:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and to this day,\Nthere's been no change whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it's the effect\Nof some kind of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,According to the doctors,\Nthere's nothing they can do at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is probably\Nmy sister's own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Imprisonment Power.\NThe power to bind all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why,\Nbut she's cast it on herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If this state continues...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,would her life be in any danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They say that if there's no change,\Nshe'll outlive you by far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can call this living, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear they found your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.45,0:20:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato Amagiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can cure your sister for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hilda Jane Rowlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman of the Tenorio Faction\Nof the Arlequint Academy Research Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm known by the people as...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magnum Opus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, I'm sorry that my father\Ncaused so much trouble in Lieseltania.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But why would your father\Ndo such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because it would inconvenience him\Nif I were to win the Gryps Festa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy, that is, rather than my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if that's the case, wasn't there\Nanother way to go about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My father must have wanted to settle things\Nbefore Galaxy made a serious move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:21:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What would befall me\Nif Galaxy were to take drastic action...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My father was all too aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Making an enemy of Galaxy is the same\Nas making an enemy of Seidoukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But even if that comes to pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention whatsoever\Nof conceding my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you all feel the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Joining my team could mean\Nmaking an enemy out of Galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I still want you all to take part\Nin the Gryps Festa with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.37,0:21:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the thought of this team\Nalluring enough to seem worth it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This lineup boasts all the best players\NI could hope for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.76,0:21:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Count me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.84,0:21:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me, too... count me in, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I saw you\Nin the last Gryps Festa,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've wanted to fight\Non your team, President!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My answer depends on Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.48,0:21:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do, Ayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.98,0:21:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no intention of asking\Nthat Magnum Opus for help,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.03,0:22:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.61,0:22:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}if there's a way to treat Big Sis...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.87,0:22:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll be joining\Nyour team, too, Claudia.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.00,0:22:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And let's win with this team!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.79,0:22:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what!
